This is a 2-player puzzle game designed and implemented by myself using Unity3D engine. Although it is made for mobile platform, Unity also support web and pc builds.

To Play:
Click on menu item to choose game mode and read tutorial
The small shapes on the player’s movable squares indicates the next bullet player can shoot.
Only bullet matching the shapes in the middle of the map can get through and attack the other player (or AI)
Player can use ‘up’ and ‘down’ to move, ‘back’ to switch bullet and ‘forward’ to shoot

Control:
Player1 = WASD
Player2 = IJKL